Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:08.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:12.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji returns to the silver screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:17.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And we give you loyal anime watchers a sneak peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's rival, the young elite Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:28.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In FKMT's works depicting the inner working of the heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:32.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,he is second only to fake Akagi as a moe character!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Playing Ichijou is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog's guaranteed not to pay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yusuke Iseya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:47.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've got to see his sneers, his shouts, his laughs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:55.17,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's great. Compared to other dramas, everything can change in a split second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:56.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shit, shit, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:59.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or that "eh" when he realizes it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:02.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of thing you can't see in other movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:08.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't miss Iseya playing the moe-moe Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:14.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji 2: Jinsei Dakkai Game, this November 5th!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:20.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and Ichijou both anticipate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:20.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　一条　それぞれの思惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:23.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who will be blessed by fate!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天が味方するのは どっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:25.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll hit it! I'll hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.71,0:01:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当てる　当てる　当てる ７億！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll hit the 700-million jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:30.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ その意気だ\Nいったれや
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}The Might of Benjamin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:34.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Win what I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の分まで勝ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:40.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘヘ　当たるわけがない\N無駄金だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Play as much as you want, Kaiji. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいぞ カイジ\N好きなだけ挑戦して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:49.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:54.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard you struggle, you can never beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:54.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうあがこうと勝てやしないんだ\Nお前は俺に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:02:01.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた！\Nそれも２段目だ　２段目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's in the second tray again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:04.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　そう ２段目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes, the second tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:07.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The second tray is the problem for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:08.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この２段目が まさに問題なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:12.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What a clever trick, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.32,0:02:12.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我ながら感心するぜ　自らのツキ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:15.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess I'm just lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しろ まったくの偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:21.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's the one who tilted the building somehow to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方なく 半ば一か八かで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴がビルを倒して作った\N奥への傾斜に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I just added to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちも かぶせていっただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:31.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That double tilt kills every ball before they make it out of the second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その過剰な奥への傾斜で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何とか２段目までで\N玉を殺そうと目論んだだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:35.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How deliciously unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが思いもかけず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完璧 最高の\Nあんばいになってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:38.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's truly the best thing I could have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:49.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,When the balls lose their momentum, they can no longer climb against the double tilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり銀玉の完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回転力が失われてくると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:49.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二重の奥への傾斜が ものをいい\Nもう上らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:53.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They fall to their deaths in the hole furthest back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:54.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉は最下点\N一番奥の穴で ほとんど死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:01.71,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But some balls have the energy left to climb just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:02.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし時には最後の力で\Nその傾斜を上る玉もある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:06.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the first tray, the next hole is a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:06.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１段目の場合\N最下点の次は当たり穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So one of every few balls makes it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 何玉かに１玉\N２段目に行く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:18.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But in the second tray, balls which avoid the depths find only another loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし２段目の場合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最下点を過ぎた玉が\Nよろよろと向かう先はハズレ穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:21.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It can't make it to the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たり穴には絶対 届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The double tilt kills them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必殺 最強の二重傾斜　ヘヘヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:35.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ！抜けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Miss the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:50.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが　気がつかんか まだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Haven't you realized yet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:57.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし よし　いけ いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ　ゼロか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:06.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They have zero capacity for learning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:06.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どいつもこいつも学習能力ゼロ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ３段目に行かないってことに\N対して何の疑問もわかないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:12.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They aren't even wondering why he's never making it to the third tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They aren't questioning that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかないのか 何の疑問も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アホタレ　分かんねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:27.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he get it? It'll never make it past the second tray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入らねえんだよ ２段目の穴は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's wasting his time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:33.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無意味ってことだ\Nいくらねばっても　ハハハ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:38.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll tell you. Since we've both tilted it inward—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:37.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてやる\Nつまり俺とお前の奥への傾斜が…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知っている\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:43.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I know that, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことは知っている 一条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But there's something that's going to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,びっくりするぜ たぶん\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:52.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The other thing this double tilt has caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:52.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二重の奥への傾斜がもたらした\Nもう１つの現象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once you see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを目の当たりにしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible! You're not even making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが\N何をわけの分からないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't try and fool me into thinking you've got something up your sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意味ありげな構えや\Nかっこつけなんかしても無駄だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その証拠に見ろ\N玉は着々と減り続けている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're losing balls as fast as you can shoot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You've only got 5 left out of the 10 million you just borrowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼みの1000万も残り500 半分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Only half!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:19.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're out of tricks now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,種切れさ\Nお前の小細工 手品の種は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　なるほど 手品か\Nそうするか いっそ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tricks, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You want tricks? I'll give you tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:29.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さん\Nセロハンテープ持ってないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you have any scotch tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I think I've got some in my briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:33.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　たぶん カバンに\N貸してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Gimme some.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい\Nはあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:38.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:45.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条　最後の最後に見せてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:48.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got one last little magic spell to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の とびっきりの秘術 魔法を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't talk too much shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ偉そうには言えないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:56.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Being able to do this is pure luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:57.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何せ これは まったくの偶然\N計算外の現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:01.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's not any talent of mine, it's more like a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神がかり的幸運　俺の力じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:07.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなら天の力\N勝負のあやってやつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:06.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's like divine power is controlling our match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:10.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\Nな… 何をする
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:11.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完成だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:16.45,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If I put this blind up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この目隠しが秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:19.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしておいて しばらく打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And keep shooting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:23.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すると あーら不思議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,霊験あらたか\N福沢諭吉の威光が道を開く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:26.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The might of Benjamin opens me a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Heaven places no man above another,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:34.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢天は人の上に人を造らず\N人の下にも人を造らず｣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,no man below another!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:39.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What I'm going on about is that the rise and fall of men is chance alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:40.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この御託の意味は 要するに\N人間の浮き沈みはチャンス次第
