Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:31.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They tilt the Bog back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:35.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし… ああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ しくじった\N致命傷か これは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I fucked it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Was that a fatal mistake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:45.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ 致命傷って　カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "fatal", Kaiji!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:51.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よれちまったんだ\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's twisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:50.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:55.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奥に倒しゃ そのまま\N素直に入るかと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:55.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought if I tilted it back they'd roll straight in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わずかなヨレ\Nミスを許さず あらがってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:21:00.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But there's just a little twist in to keep that from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身をよじって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりを防ぎにきた\N機械のくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:05.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This damn machine is twisted to make sure no one wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:11.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔だ　こいつはやっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:11.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It really is a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食い殺される
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's swallowing me whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の 最後の 最後の土壇場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the final, final, final moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,牙をむく沼　逆襲 逆襲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:24.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog bares its fangs and counterattacks! Counterattacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人食い沼の逆襲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:27.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the Man-eating Bog counterattacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:35.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Proverbs of Kaiji Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:49.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Heaven places no man above another, no man below another!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:56.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What I'm going on about is that the rise and fall of men is chance alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:03.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Even a fool or scum has a chance to win!
